      "text": "Routes to Fabric\nWorkspace B via\nPrivate Endpoint",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "9h02ubSoFx1T9DIrnRc6V",
      "originalText": "Routes to Fabric Workspace B via Private Endpoint",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "KibgclHi1cORjfiZvZXAG",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 375.2756313379539,
      "y": 1168.9650149772483,
      "width": 896.5993041992188,
      "height": 425,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "al",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 221437086,
      "version": 592,
      "versionNonce": 2059687621,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773841721763,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Notes:\nPrivate Endpoints don't have to be in the same subnet.  Could use one subnet and call \nit FabricPrivateEndpoints and put all private endpoints for Fabric Workspaces here,\nwhich is easier to manage but could become a large subnet\nOr\n\nPreferred:\ncould setup different subnets based on team, maybe ResearchTeamAFabricPrivateEndpoints\n(or something much better named than that)\n\nPrivate Endpoints have a cost meter against them\n\n\n\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Notes:\nPrivate Endpoints don't have to be in the same subnet.  Could use one subnet and call \nit FabricPrivateEndpoints and put all private endpoints for Fabric Workspaces here,\nwhich is easier to manage but could become a large subnet\nOr\n\nPreferred:\ncould setup different subnets based on team, maybe ResearchTeamAFabricPrivateEndpoints\n(or something much better named than that)\n\nPrivate Endpoints have a cost meter against them\n\n\n\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
